.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-2-2::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: cooking, drawing, singing, woodworking
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: action, adventure, scientific, western
City: rome, new-york, edinburgh, marseilles
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: ice-hockey, lacrosse, swimming, water-polo
1. the person who's sport is water-polo is on the right of the person who's hobby is woodworking##1
2. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the far right##1
3. the person traveling to marseilles is the person who's sport is lacrosse##1
4. the person who's hobby is singing is on the right of the person who's hobby is drawing##1
5. the person watching western movies is between the person traveling to edinburgh and the person who's sport is ice-hockey##2
6. the person who's sport is water-polo is between the person watching western movies and the person traveling to marseilles##2
7. the person traveling to rome is on the far right##1
8. the person watching adventure movies is on the left of the person who's hobby is singing##1
9. the person watching scientific movies is on the right of the person traveling to new-york##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |    3     |     4      |
| Hobby         | woodworking | drawing    | singing  | cooking    |
| Movie-Genre   | action      | adventure  | western  | scientific |
| City           | marseilles      | edinburgh       | new-york      | rome       |
| Sport         | lacrosse    | water-polo | swimming | ice-hockey |

