.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-2-3::.
There 4 different types of food: artichoke, blueberry, lemon, mango
The people have 4 different hobbies: camping, fishing, photography, traveling
The people have 4 different jobs:  analyst, lawyer, paramedic, pilot
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: july, november, may, october
1. the paramedic is the person who's birthday is in november##1
2. the person who's birthday is in november is on the left of the pilot##1
3. the person who's birthday is in may is on the left of the person who's birthday is in november##1
4. the person who's birthday is in november is on the left of the person who's birthday is in july##1
5. the person eating lemon is on the left of the person who's hobby is photography##1
6. the lawyer is the person who's hobby is traveling##1
7. the person eating mango is on the right of the person who's hobby is photography##1
8. the person eating artichoke is between the person who's hobby is camping and the person who's hobby is traveling##2
9. the person who's hobby is photography is between the person eating lemon and the lawyer##2

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |     2     |      3      |     4     |
| Food        | blueberry | lemon     | artichoke   | mango     |
| Hobby       | fishing   | camping   | photography | traveling |
| Job         | analyst   | paramedic | pilot       | lawyer    |
| Birthday   | may    | november | july  | october    |

