 4. the security-guard is on the left of the person who's sport is sailing##1
 5. the cain-smoker is on the left of the person eating peach##1
 6. the person eating lemon is on the left of the cain-smoker##1
 7. the social-worker is on the left of the person eating asparagus##1
 8. the lawyer is the swisher-smoker##1
 9. the person eating lemon is between the person who's sport is weightlifting and the bongani-smoker##2
10. the ritmeester-smoker is the person who's sport is sailing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1        |       2       |       3       |     4      |
| Food          | garlic         | lemon         | asparagus     | peach      |
| Job           | security-guard | social-worker | freelancer    | lawyer     |
| Cigar   | bongani      | ritmeester       | cain    | swisher       |
