 1. the person who likes grey is on the right of the fan of blues##1
 2. the person watching fantasy movies is the dutch##1
 3. the fan of dubstep is between the dutch and the person who likes coral##2
 4. the fan of metal is the person who likes grey##1
 5. the russian is on the left of the person watching zombie movies##1
 6. the person watching fantasy movies is on the left of the person who likes amber##1
 7. the argentine is the person who likes brown##1
 8. the fan of soul is on the far right##1
 9. the person watching fantasy movies is on the right of the person watching time-travel movies##1
10. the dutch is the person who likes grey##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |    3    |    4    |
| Movie-Genre   | time-travel | fantasy | family  | zombie  |
| Music-Genre   | blues       | metal   | dubstep | soul    |
| Nationality   | argentine   | dutch   | russian | british |
| Color     | brown    | grey   | amber    | coral  |

