There 4 different types of food: corn, nectarine, onion, plum
The people have 4 different hobbies: filmmaking, hiking, photography, woodworking
4 different pets are kept: dog, horse, rat, turtle
 1. the person traveling to berlin is on the right of the person traveling to london##1
 2. the owner of the dog is on the right of the owner of the rat##1
 3. the person who's hobby is hiking is on the right of the person who's hobby is woodworking##1
 4. the person eating corn is the person traveling to london##1
 5. the person traveling to edinburgh is on the right of the person traveling to hamburg##1
 6. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is on the right of the person eating corn##1
 7. the owner of the rat is on the left of the person traveling to edinburgh##1
 8. the owner of the turtle is between the person eating corn and the person eating onion##2
 9. the person eating plum is on the right of the owner of the horse##1
10. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is between the person eating corn and the person eating onion##2

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |     2      |      3      |       4       |
| City   | london    | berlin    | hamburg      | edinburgh |
| Food       | corn        | plum       | onion       | nectarine     |
| Hobby      | photography | filmmaking | woodworking | hiking        |
| Pet        | horse       | turtle     | rat         | dog           |

